com.intellij.diagram

Class DiagramProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.diagram.DiagramProvider<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.intellij.openapi.project.PossiblyDumbAware
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseDiagramProvider

    public abstract class DiagramProvider<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.intellij.openapi.project.PossiblyDumbAware
    Use com.intellij.diagram.Provider extension point to implement diagramming support for a framework, language or technology. Use BaseDiagramProvider class as a base for small and simple diagrams
    Author:
    Konstantin Bulenkov
    See Also:
    BaseDiagramProvider
